				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Raphael is encountered at the beginning of the Shar Temple. He briefs the player about the Orthon - the devil he mentions - either telling them that he personally wants it dead, or that it is between the player and their objective. He then saves them from a trap and warns them about the dangers of the temple, before vanishing.\r\n\r\n!!! Don't remove REALLY_ASTARION tag check from the OOM branch!!!"
				}
